text: Eunidia quadrialbovittata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1961. It is known from Ethiopia.BioLib.cz - Eunidia quadrialbovittata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1961
title: Eunidia quadrialbovittata
